quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  38,65,"Ini: \"nek, d aneddaĂŽ kan. Ur illi ĂŽebbi siwa Ăebbi, Yiwen, AqehhaĂŽ"
  38,66,"Mass n tmurt, igenwan, akked wayen illan garasen, Uzmir IpsemmiĂȘen"
  38,67,"Ini: \"d asali ameqwĂŽahan"
  38,68,"Kunwi, teooam t"
  38,69,"Ur illi wayen Ă©ĂŽi$ $eĂŽ le$wat aĂąlayen meĂŽĂŽa, mi mqellaĂąn"
  38,70,"PpuweĂȘĂȘa$ d kan, ar nek d aneddaĂŽ ipbegginen"
  38,71,"Mi Inna Mass ik i lmalayek: \"Nek ad Xelqe$ amdan, si talaxt"
  38,72,"Mi t Mesle$, Suve$ degs, si ĂŽĂŽuĂȘ iW, Ăźinzemt $uĂŽes, s lekni"
  38,73,"Knant akw lmalayek, akken ma llant"
  38,74,"siwa Iblis i izuxxen, illa seg ijehliyen"
  38,75,"Inna: \"A Iblis, w ik igedlen lekni i win Xelqe$ s ifassen iW? Tzuxxev, ne$ telliv seg wid iufraren"
  38,76,"Inna: \"Nek ife$ t. Txelqev iyi si tmes, Txelqev t si talaxt"
  38,77,"Inna: \"Effe$ segs, keĂ§Ă§ d imenfi"
  38,78,"Inna: \"fellak xezzu, alamma d ass iqeĂźĂźiyen"
  38,79,"Inna: \"A Mass iw, eoo iyi ar ass ideg ara d kkren"
  38,80,"Inna: \"keĂ§Ă§, ih, seg wid Ooi"
  38,81,ar ass n wukud ipwassnen
  38,82,"Inna: \"s tezmert iK, a ten $ewwu$, akken ma llan"
  38,83,siwa imdanen iK izedganen segsen
  38,84,"Inna: \"tidep, d tidep ay Nni"
  38,85,"Ad Acare$ Loahennama yissek, akked wid, segsen, i k ivefĂŽen, akken ma llan"
  38,86,"Ini: \"ur awen ssutre$ taqdiĂąt af waya. Ur lli$, nek, seg wid ippestaĂąmilen"
  38,87,"Neppa, s tidep, d asmekti kan i imavalen"
  38,88,"Mi tĂąadda tallit, war ccekk, a kwen id iawev usali s"